<TEXT>
a 12yearold girl slain outside a housing 
project the 16th child shot in new york city in two months may 
have been killed in revenge rather than at random police said 
tuesday 
laykama taylor whose nickname was sugar spent her last 
days in fear of retaliation for a street fight neighbors told 
police 
theyre going to shoot me theyre going to get me laykama 
had told a friend who was interviewed by detectives said a police 
source told the associated press speaking on condition of 
anonymity 
the young girl was fatally shot in the back sunday afternoon as 
she sat on a bench braiding a friends hair outside a housing 
project in the city borough of brooklyn another young girl was 
shot at the same project on monday 
in all 16 children have been shot in new york city since july 
22 police said laykama was the sixth to die 
police initially described laykamas shooting as accidental but 
the daily news on tuesday quoted police saying revenge was the 
motive detective lt robert ceccarini disputed that report 
tuesday 
laykama had argued with another 12yearold girl on thursday 
and older boys from both of the girls families became involved in 
the fight police said 
we do know there was prior disputes involving her and a 
girlfriend and they made up and brothers got involved pushing 
and shoving ceccarini said but as far as that being a motive 
we havent uncovered that 
the young men involved in the fight were questioned by police 
and remain suspects in the shooting ceccarini said 
laykama was shot from an upper floor or the roof of the project 
as she sat in a courtyard filled with playing children detectives 
were awaiting ballistics tests but said they believed the killer 
used a 9mm handgun 
that wasnt a stray that bullet was meant for her said the 
girls aunt pee taylor 
as police investigated laykamas shooting a 13yearold girl 
was shot in the head monday night while sitting on a bench in the 
same housing project she was hospitalized in stable condition 
earlier sunday a 15yearold girl was shot in the leg as she 
stood with a group of friends in brooklyn a 12yearold girl was 
shot friday while playing in a harlem playground 
</TEXT>
