we still believe we have an undercount despite that she 
said 
the officials came from cities as small as meridian miss and 
as large as los angeles but all 21 cities represented have filed 
challenges to the census bureaus preliminary population estimates 
they are driven by the fact that the greater their population 
the more federal aid they will receive population also determines 
how many representatives they will have in congress 
