people from lower castes who have been downtrodden for centuries 
by indias rigid caste system 
another 225 percent of the coveted jobs already were kept aside 
for what the government described as the most backward castes and 
native tribes five to 10 percent of jobs are proposed to be 
reserved for the poor irrespective of caste 
the move triggered a wave of protests by uppercaste students 
who say it will deprive them of job opportunities at least 25 
people have died in battles with police and a score have attempted 
suicide by setting themselves ablaze 
