that poor school districts would have accepted clements killed 
that proposal by vetoing the taxes needed to pay for it 
its entirely because of gov clements footdragging and the 
republican legislators who upheld his veto that were back in the 
court again and were literally about to turn over the keys of the 
schoolroom to the courts colbert said 
