groups from adhering to the governments position of peace 
gaviria said 
there was no immediate response from the two main rebel groups 
that gavirias statment was aimed at the national liberation army 
and the colombian revolutionary armed forces 
the groups have been fighting in the mountains and jungles of 
colombia for more than 20 years their attacks contribute to a 
climate of violence that includes murders and kidnappings by 
rightwing death squads and drug smugglers 
the ceasefire would be the first step toward convincing the 
guerrillas to disband and form civilian groups to participate in 
the countrys politics 
