limited partners of the funds 
mccormick capitals subsidiary mccormick futures management 
inc will become general partner and commodity pool operator of 
the funds advanced portfolio management limited partnership ii 
stotler futures fund stotler heartland futures fund i thomson 
commodity partners i thomson commodity partners ii thomson 
financial futures partners i and thomson mckinnon futures fund 
the federal bankruptcy court suspended proceedings against 
stotler group to allow mccormick to assume control of the funds 
