the environmental benefits of atlantic 
richfield cos new premium unleaded gasoline outweigh any possible 
health risks suggested by private tests scientists said 
the tests indicate the gasoline designed to reduce pollutants 
produces a 34 percent increase in emissions of a suspected 
carcinogen 
but scientists said the fuels overall benefits to clean air and 
health are worthwhile and the increased concentrations of 
13butadiene were too small to pose a health threat 
i dont personally think the emissions are anything to worry 
