paramount communications inc raised 
its offer tuesday for the 17 percent of tvx broadcast group inc 
stock it does not own to 950 a share from 750 and the tvx 
board of directors recommended the offer 
new yorkbased paramount already owns 83 percent of tvx stock 
tvx owns and operates six independent television stations 
