million under the initial offer for the roughly 71 million shares 
paramount does not own 
completion of the transaction is subject to negotiating an 
acquisition agreement and to approval of tvx shareholders at a 
yettobe scheduled meeting 
a special committee of independent tvx directors recommended 
acceptance of the latest proposal and the board accepted that 
recommendation 
